===收视率===
《豪斯的头》于2008年5月12日通过福克斯在美国首播<ref name="BTV2">{{cite news |url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/part-1-of-house-season-finale-19294.aspx |title=Part 1 of 'House' Season Finale Airs Tonight |author=Santagio, Rosario |publisher=''BuddyTV'' |date=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329013736/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/part-1-of-house-season-finale-19294.aspx |archivedate=2012-03-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，有约1484万户家庭观看，在18-49岁年龄段人群中拥有5.8 / 14%的收视率<ref name="TVBN night" />，是当晚所有电视节目的收视亚军，仅次于《[[舞动奇迹_(真人秀)|舞动奇迹]]》<ref name="TVBN night">{{cite news |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/05/13/nielsen-ratings-may-12-foxs-house-most-watched-among-youth/3747/ |title=Nielsen Ratings May 12: FOX’s ‘House’ Most Watched Among Youth |author=Seidman, Robert |date=2008-05-13 |publisher=''TV by the Numbers'' |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905222157/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/05/13/nielsen-ratings-may-12-foxs-house-most-watched-among-youth/3747/ |archivedate=2012-09-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。而在2008年5月11至18号这一星期内，《豪斯的头》是收视率第9高的电视节目<ref name="ABCm">{{cite web |publisher=''ABC Medianet'' |date=2008-05-06 |url=http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050608_02 |title=Weekly Program Rankings |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210142818/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=050608_02 |archivedate=2012-02-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="TVBN week">{{cite news |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/05/20/american-idol-dancing-with-the-stars-and-csi-lead-weekly-nielsen-ratings/3846/ |title=American Idol, Dancing with the Stars and CSI Lead Weekly Nielsen Ratings |author=Seidman, Robert |date=2008-05-20 |publisher=''TV by the Numbers'' |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120911044022/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/05/20/american-idol-dancing-with-the-stars-and-csi-lead-weekly-nielsen-ratings/3846/ |archivedate=2012-09-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。如果加上通过标清电视等途径，观众人数将达到1502万<ref name="TVBN week" />。本集于2008年5月12日在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]首播，观众人数为143.2万，是当晚收视人数第二高的节目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/05/the_who_we_are_2.html |title=The Who We Are Update: Nine back on top |last=Dale |first=David |date=2008-05-16 |publisher=''The Sun-Herald'' |accessdate=2008-05-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322082442/http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/05/the_who_we_are_2.html |archivedate=2012-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《豪斯的头》还于5月12日在[[加拿大|加拿大]]播出<ref name="BMM" />，观众人数为229.6万，是该周收视率第4高的节目，落后于《[[实习医生格蕾|实习医生格蕾]]》和《[[美國偶像|美國偶像]]》<ref name="BMM">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05122008.pdf |publisher=''Bureau of Broadcasting Measurement Canada'' |date=2008-05-12 |title=Top Programs–Total Canada (English) |accessdate=2008-10-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319223347/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05122008.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2008年6月26日，《豪斯的头》通过第5频道在英国播出，有170万人观看<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.channel5.com/shows/house/episodes/houses-head |title=Episode 15: House's Head |publisher=Five |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719171729/http://www.channel5.com/shows/house/episodes/houses-head |archivedate=2013-07-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2008/jun/27/tvratings.television |title=TV Ratings: Spain's Euro 2008 victory over Russia watched by 7 million |publisher=''the guardian'' |date=2008-06-27 |author=Holmwood, Leigh |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113224013/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2008/jun/27/tvratings.television |archivedate=2012-11-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

===专业评价===
[[Image:Omar_Epps.jpg|thumb]]

《豪斯的头》总体上获得了评论员较为正面的评价<ref name="LAT" /><ref name="EW1" />。莎拉·莫里森（{{lang|en|Sara Morrison}}）称豪斯恢复[[记忆|记忆]]的段落是“你能在电视上所看到的最完美的10分钟”<ref name="TWoP">{{cite news |url=http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/show/house/houses_head.php |title=Busted |date=2008-05-19 |author=Morrison, Sara |publisher=''Television Without Pity'' |accessdate=2008-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222041546/http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/show/house/houses_head.php |archivedate=2012-02-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。她也对催眠戏段感到满意，因为这让蔡斯“有事可干”。莫里森给剧集的评级为A+<ref name="TWoP" />。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的米歇尔·罗梅罗（{{lang|en|Michelle Romero}}）认为把《豪斯的头》重新看一遍也仍然会像第一次看时感觉那么好<ref name="EW1">{{cite news |first=Michelle |last=Romero |date=2008-05-13 |url=http://tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/house-recap-season4-episode15/ |title='House': Head Case |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001111345/http://tvrecaps.ew.com/recap/house-recap-season4-episode15/ |archivedate=2012-10-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|電視指南]]的吉娜·汀努诺（{{lang|en|Gina Dinunno}}）称这一集“有我所想像的一切，辉煌、高调、混乱，甚至有些下流！他们最后的悬念真是设置得太好了，我们都迫不及待地想要看看安柏到底怎么样了。”<ref name="TVG1">{{cite news |url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/house/episode-15-season-4/100213 |title=House's Head |author=Dinunno, Gina |date=2008-05-13 |publisher=''TV Guild'' |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007152652/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/house/episode-15-season-4/100213 |archivedate=2012-10-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。阿兰·塞平沃尔（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}）把这一季与[[豪斯医生_(第2季)|第2季]]的结局《[[没有理由|没有理由]]》相比<ref>{{cite news |url=http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/05/all_tv_amanda_from_mtvs_the_pa.html |title=All TV: Amanda from MTV's 'The Paper' speaks, 'House' review |publisher=''The Star Ledger'' |author=Sepinwall, Alan |date=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829172554/http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/05/all_tv_amanda_from_mtvs_the_pa.html |archivedate=2012-08-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，觉得《豪斯的头》中存在“几个问题”，主要是剧情中有关“答案”就是安柏的隐射。他认为《豪斯医生》本质上来说还是个谜，并不是一部娱乐性的作品<ref>{{cite news |url=http://sepinwall.blogspot.com/2008/05/house-houses-head-fly-in-ointment.html |title=House, "House's Head": Fly in the ointment |author=Sepinwall, Alan |publisher=''The Star-Ledger'' |date=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604222126/http://sepinwall.blogspot.com/2008/05/house-houses-head-fly-in-ointment.html |archivedate=2012-06-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}的詹姆斯·张伯伦（{{lang|en|James Chamberlin}}）表示希望这季结局的后半部分可以达到前半部分的高度<ref name="IGN">{{cite news |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/05/13/house-houses-head-review |title=House: "House's Head" Review |author=Chamberlin, James |publisher=''[[IGN|IGN]]'' |date=2008-05-13 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217065246/http://tv.ign.com/articles/873/873496p1.html |archivedate=2012-02-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，他还表示剧中有关“答案”的内容让他想到了《[[黑客帝国|黑客帝国]]》。张伯伦给了这一集9.5的高分（最高10分）<ref name="IGN" />。芭芭拉·巴内特（{{lang|en|Barbara Barnett}}）称赞了休·劳瑞和莉萨·埃德尔斯坦的表演<ref name="BC" />，她还表示虽然这一集中有许多“令人难忘的瞬间”，但其中撞车的镜头实在是“激烈”、“充满张力”得让人“心跳都要停止”了<ref name="BC">{{cite news |url=http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/05/15/0708284.php |title=TV Review: House, MD - "House's Head" |date=2008-05-15 |publisher=''Blog Critics'' |author=Barnett, Barbara |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090410212558/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/05/15/0708284.php |archivedate=2009-04-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。詹妮弗·古德温认为《豪斯的头》可以轻易成为《豪斯医生》最出色的季终篇<ref>{{cite news |title=House Boss David Shore: Everybody Lies, Everybody Dies, Everybody... |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/13489/house-boss-david-shore-everybody-lies-everybody-dies-everybody |author=Godwin, Jennifer |publisher=''E!'' |date=2008-05-21 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929064524/http://www.eonline.com/news/13489/house-boss-david-shore-everybody-lies-everybody-dies-everybody |archivedate=2012-09-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外，还有多位评论员对弗里德·德斯特客串酒保的短暂露面感到惊喜<ref name="EW1" /><ref name="TWoP" />。

丽莎·卡迪跳脱衣舞的段落也获得了评论员较为正面的评价<ref name="BTV1">{{cite news |url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/part-2-of-house-season-finale-19517.aspx |title=Part 2 of 'House' Season Finale Airs Tonight |author=Santiago, Rosario |date=2008-05-19 |publisher=''BuddyTV'' |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329013700/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/part-2-of-house-season-finale-19517.aspx |archivedate=2012-03-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Z2i">{{cite news |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/ithappenedlastnight/2008/05/house-crashing.html |title='House' Crashing realities |author=Paff, Jessica |date=2008-05-12 |publisher=''Zap2it'' |accessdate=2009-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090105222935/http://blog.zap2it.com/ithappenedlastnight/2008/05/house-crashing.html |archivedate=2009-01-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的玛丽·麦克纳玛（{{lang|en|Mary McNarma}}）称这段“三分钟的镜头让{{lang|en|[[TiVo|TiVo]]}}的钱花得值了”<ref name="LAT">{{cite news |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2008/05/now-thats-a-bit.html |title='House': What goes on inside that good doctor's head? |author=McNarma, Mary |publisher=''Los Angeles Times'' |date=2008-05-13 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925091646/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2008/05/now-thats-a-bit.html |archivedate=2012-09-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|IGN}}的詹姆斯·张伯伦表示自己从没想到过埃德尔斯坦真会跳一段脱衣舞，虽说他曾这样希望过<ref name="IGN" />。在这一季所发行DVD的评论音轨中，杰西·斯宾塞、莉萨·埃德尔斯坦、安妮·达德克、[[珍妮花·摩利遜|珍妮花·摩利遜]]和[[欧玛·艾普斯|欧玛·艾普斯]]都表示《豪斯医生》中他们最喜欢的一集就是《豪斯的头》<ref name="DVDC">{{cite video|people=Laurie, Hugh; Shore, David; Edelstein, Lisa; Spencer, Jesse, Jennifer Marie Morrison, Anne Dudek & Epps, Omar|title=House, Season 4, My Favorite Episode So Far...|medium=DVD|publisher=Universal|date=2008-08-19|accessdate=2008-10-18}}</ref>。

===奖项===
莉萨·埃德尔斯坦、杰西·斯宾塞和休·劳瑞分别参与了[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]杰出正剧类剧集女配角奖、杰出正剧类剧集男配角奖和杰出正剧类剧集男主角奖的角逐<ref name="EMMY08">{{cite news |title=2008 Emmy Awards Campaigns & Episode Submissions (Part 1) |date=2008-03-25 |url=http://goldderbyforums.latimes.com/eve/forums/a/tpc/f/1106078764/m/340102161 |publisher=The Envelope Forum, Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2008-10-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080401002447/http://goldderbyforums.latimes.com/eve/forums/a/tpc/f/1106078764/m/340102161 |archivedate=2008-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，彼得·布莱克、[[大卫·沃尔特·福斯特|大卫·沃尔特·福斯特]]、拉塞尔·弗伦德、加里特·莱纳和多丽丝·伊根也参加了黄金时段艾美奖杰出正剧类编剧奖角逐<ref name="EMMY08" />，导演格雷格·艾坦尼斯获得了正剧类剧集杰出导演奖提名<ref name="EMMY08" />，之后休·劳瑞也成功获得了提名<ref name="Emmynoms08">{{cite web |publisher=''Academy of Television Arts & Sciences'' |date=2008-06-17 |url=http://cdn.emmys.tv/awards/2008pte/60thpte_noms.php |title=Complete 2008 Nominations List |accessdate=2009-09-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120719130934/http://cdn.emmys.tv/awards/2008pte/60thpte_noms.php |archivedate=2012-07-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。最终艾坦尼斯成功胜出，但劳瑞不敌主演{{lang|en|AMC}}剧集《[[絕命毒師|絕命毒師]]》的布莱恩·科兰斯顿<ref name="08emmywinners" />。

